div.h3: Distance learning in Juvenile Court Schools

strong.span: To help limit the spread of COVID-19, the Los Angeles County Office of Education has closed its offices to the public and asked staff to work from home. We monitor voicemail and emails daily and will do our best to reply immediately. Please visit our COVID-19
for guidance and resources. We will provide updates as new information becomes available. Thank you for your continued support and compassion during this difficult time.
